/div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h3><strong>Business Meeting</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n<u>Our business meeting will be held in the conference room at the Iowa State facility . Agenda items include: </u>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n1. Treasurerâ€™s Report\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n2. Meeting Site Update\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n3. Spring Auction Update\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n4. Non - profit Status Update\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n5. Website Update\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\n6. Election\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h3><strong>Dinner at Bufordâ€™s Restaurant</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nA room has been reserved at Bufordâ€™s Restaurant for those club members that would like to go out to eat after the tour and meeting. Bufordâ€™s is the restaurant at the Quality Inn &amp; Suites (used to be the Starlight Motel) on 13 th Street next to the i nterstate . We believe the tour and business meeting should be adjourned around 7:00 p.m.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 4\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n\r\nWe can compare notes about our bees and answer our new club memberâ€™s questions. For the new beekeepers and members â€“ bring those questions ; f or the â€œold timersâ€ bring the answers .\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Club Leaders</h3>\r\nMike Sanders, President\r\n\r\nTBA, Vice President\r\n\r\nJulia McGuire, __________\r\n\r\nMargaret Hala, ___________\r\n\r\nJamie Beyer, ____________\r\n\r\nJolene Eriksen, __________\r\n\r\nValerie Just, Treasurer and Beeline Editor\r\n\r\nArvin Foell, ___________\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Members', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-28 23:25:52', '2017-11-28 23:25:52', '', 23, 'http://beckjohnsonart.com/ciba/2017/11/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
